description: The Fund seeks daily investment results, before fees and expenses, of 2 times (200%) the daily percentage change of the common stock of Alibaba Group Holding Limited, (NASDAQ: BABA) There is no guarantee that the Fund will meet its stated objective. The fund should not be expected to provide 2 times the cumulative return of BABA for periods greater than a day.
name: GraniteShares 2x Long BABA Daily ETF
